This women’s day @nitya.arora @lilymarinabaria & @sincerely_sherlyn & I got together with @elleindia to create something fun over music, dance, food, drinks & fashion, ofcourse! node.text:
Your girl killed it this year, sis! Just wrapped up my last travel collaboration for the year and I feel so overwhelmed with my journey! It’s been amazing, there's been so much of unlearning & learning and yet it still feels like it’s just the beginning! 😍 The spiritual journey has been nothing but amazing, my approach to lot of things has changed, and it’ll keep changing with different life experiences... it’s a journey to let go & grow 🙏🏼❤️
Thank you for all the love and support from each one of you! To all the brands I have collaborated with this year, a BIG THANK YOU for believing in me! My team, friends and family of course are my spirit animals! And more than anything, I thank my body for keeping up with the hustle at all times! ❤ THANK YOU for giving me energy to do this! Now I’m pretty excited for my personal holiday, FINALLY! 💥😍Where the memo would be to CHILLL and kill it with basics, probably wear the same outfit for a couple of days 😆❤
I have missed that and how!!!! Enjoy the last few days of 2019!!! KILLLL IT, I LOVE Y’ALL ❤ 🙏🏼 ||
🎵 Also used my one of my favourite tracks for this one - Enough to Believe ( Bob Moses, Jamie Jones Remix ) @jamiejonesmusic BIG FAN 💘
